title: Tiffany's on Vine Comedy Night
desc: Brian Moreno  and  Jay Davis  team up to bring you a sexy night of FREE comedy in Hollywood. Jay Davis is the premier comedy producer in LA and this night is guaranteed to be hilarious. Brian Moreno is a long time comedian and created House of Blues Comedy and  StrictlyHumor.com . Every Wednesday night top headliners from all over the country in an intimate venue that you will not forget! Come out and laugh.
